                     <interp inst="t18230910-84-off478" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230910-84-cd479" type="crimeDate">20th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230910-84-off478 t18230910-84-cd479"></join>, thirty-three books, value 5 l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18230910-84-victim950" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Barnes
                        <interp inst="t18230910-84-victim950" type="surname" value="Barnes"></interp>
